App name: Jimmy Brings

Brief: Jimmy Brings is an innovative app providing the convenience of having your favorite drinks and snacks delivered right to your doorstep. Built around the promise of prompt and responsible alcohol delivery, it caters to those looking to enjoy a great night in without the hassle of stepping out. With a fixed delivery rate and a cold drink guarantee, it's positioned as a go-to service for anyone above the age of 18 looking to responsibly purchase alcoholic and other beverages.
